Here is an example exported image with a thumbnail: 

{noformat}
<p><span class="image-wrap" style=""><a class="confluence-thumbnail-link 500x466" href='http://localhost:8080/confluence/download/attachments/2457648/river.jpg'><img src="attachments/thumbnails/2457648/2785284" width="100" style="border: 0px solid black"/></a></span></p>
