We are currently building a space which serves to display industry news (clipped from newsletters) filtered by various criteria. For this purpose we use {blog-posts} with associated labels and match-labels=all to allow for detailed filtering of the displayed news.
In parallel we also intended to offer the news-content of each page as RSS-feed; this is however not possible in the more advanced filter cases, since the feed-builder only supports disjunction of labels.

