I just recently upgraded our confluence install, and then updated all our plugins.  And when the plugin repository showed all green, I thought I was done. 

Turns out that the Builder plugin requires an up-to-date version of the "Page Information Tools" plugin.    Except I guess the version I had was so old, it was reporting as "Unknown Version".   But... it was too subtle for me to see it until I was pointed right at it.  

My request then, is to have any plugin with 'Uknown version' cause that row, or that Status column to highlight with a color, to make it stand out as being potentially problematic.    Green means good,  yellow means update, red should mean 'look at this - problem here'.

