Currently there is no way to look up a user in admin and see what space(s) they have access to. You have to do things in reverse to get that information, i.e. check every space and note what user/groups are enabled, then cross-check it against the user and his/her own groups.

Would be nice to have a section, visible on viewuser.action or linked from that page, that supplied this information.

This would help IMMENSELY in identifying what problems a user is seeing. When someone points out a problem, we always start with the user record and work backwards.

